14:T484,| # | G'oya | Taxminiy diapazon | Kimga mos |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Gravirovkali soat | $250-$500+ | Top rahbar, kalit hamkor |
| 2 | Premium ruchka + quti | $50-$200 | Rahbar, decision-maker |
| 3 | Desk set (yog'och/metall) | $120-$350 | Rahbar, bo'lim boshlig'i |
| 4 | VIP gift box (3-6 buyum) | $150-$450 | Hamkorlar, mijozlar |
| 5 | Termos premium (nomli) | $40-$150 | Mijoz/hamkor |
| 6 | Vizitka qutisi (metall) | $30-$120 | B2B aloqa |
| 7 | Powerbank premium | $60-$200 | Safar qiladigan hamkor |
| 8 | Planner + aksessuarlar seti | $50-$180 | Decision-maker |
| 9 | Mini-bar / aksessuar qutisi (neytral) | $120-$300 | VIP hamkor (etikka mos) |
| 10 | Yog'och qutida choy/kofe set | $80-$220 | Ofis protokoli |
| 11 | Brendli "welcome for partner" set | $90-$250 | Yangi hamkor |
| 12 | Metall brelok premium | $15-$70 | Qisqa uchrashuv/komplement |
| 13 | Notbuk stendi premium | $70-$220 | Tech hamkor |
| 14 | Konferensiya VIP seti | $60-$200 | Event, ko'rgazma VIP |
| 15 | Individual konsept (custom) | $200-$600+ | Alohida protokol holatlari |
